---
title: Tex-Mex Pork Enchilada Bowls Tex-Mex Pork Enchilada Bowls
description: Rice bowls are way beyond “having a moment” and have officially transformed into a dinnertime staple. And why not? They’re hearty, flavorful, and so versatile. This version’s got bold ’n’ saucy pork served over a bed of fluffy lime rice, topped with fresh salsa, pepper jack, and Southwest crema. Yep, this bodacious bowl is sure to satisfy.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/tex-mex-pork-enchilada-bowls-2138e5bd.jpg
